Package: sleep-manager
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.11), python3-venv, python3-pip, sudo, systemd, etherwake, ethtool
Description: Two-machine sleep/wake control over HTTP
 Sleep Manager provides sleeper and waker roles in a single Flask service
 to suspend a machine and send Wake-on-LAN packets on a trusted LAN.
